title: 20th Annual UCLA Healthcare Symposium
desc: Digitized Medicine: There's an App for That! The advent and rapid proliferation of digital sensors and health monitoring smartphone technology in the hands of the consumer holds incredible promise. Join us as we explore the evolving roles of physicians and patients in the age where patients are utilizing smartphone technology to become active participants in managing their own health and disease.
